{"tid":2125221,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新垃圾桶悄悄現身　「佛系」展示「Minions」版本","createTime":"2020-07-26T04:54:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-26T12:12:42.000Z","uid":27530,"like":6,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ab2afa1eae3ec00748515bb332f2619ffe95fe80","tid":2125221,"uid":27530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T04:54:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BtX9CF0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBtX9CF0.jpg&h=bbbc5dae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n環保署本月11日起在綠在區區默默展開巡迴展覽，新設計有多項改良，包括改用拉門設計、煙灰缸改用傾倒式設計或用鐵鍊連接可整個提取、大型垃圾桶可用腳踏開蓋、選用可回收物料製作等，更有被笑指似「Minions」的新垃圾桶。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/498986/新垃圾桶悄悄現身-佛系-展示-minions-版本-惟眼看手勿動\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F498986%2F%E6%96%B0%E5%9E%83%E5%9C%BE%E6%A1%B6%E6%82%84%E6%82%84%E7%8F%BE%E8%BA%AB-%E4%BD%9B%E7%B3%BB-%E5%B1%95%E7%A4%BA-minions-%E7%89%88%E6%9C%AC-%E6%83%9F%E7%9C%BC%E7%9C%8B%E6%89%8B%E5%8B%BF%E5%8B%95&d=OqPbpPrVkTbcBhMc%2F4HaLgoLTLCpuPbPc66RZsxrzrI%3D&h=1c993285\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/498986/新垃圾桶悄悄現身-佛系-展示-minions-版本-惟眼看手勿動</a>"},{"pid":"1f7acd411a7dfae61330306e36601f0b8e82878b","tid":2125221,"uid":27530,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T04:58:45.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"7ccd8256a2c8978120b0af77b262c93fdb2d9853","tid":2125221,"uid":152589,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T04:59:22.000Z","msg":"笨娜娜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44c1f7cc9ac01c4d947a7708c008bf79a3e7b9b0","tid":2125221,"uid":61882,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T05:06:24.000Z","msg":"咩人會po支那01既link<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1568cc1991df0c898a13a24ec3fb6c657826d0f9","tid":2125221,"uid":27530,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7ccd825